			<Question qid="0002367-1" qtype="information">Do you have information about Leg or foot amputation</Question>
			<Answer>Leg or foot amputation is the removal of a leg, foot or toes from the body. These body parts are called extremities. Amputations are done either by surgery or they occur by accident or trauma to the body.</Answer>
